        "subject": "LU-10938 wbc: Basic symlink support",
        "message": "LU-10938 wbc: Basic symlink support\n\nThis compiles and works, but not ideal, due to some\nhacks around rpc formats on the server and we don't want\nto return locks for symlinks after creates and such.\n\nThere's unknown error coming from lmv for who knows why,\nwhen we do async symlink create:\n\"(lmv_obd.c:275:lmv_init_ea_size())\nlustre-clilmv-ffff8800cd4ee800: NULL export for 0\"\n\nDown not appear to be breaking anything in a visible way,\nthough.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nChange-Id: I3f75d651b8d5c8c6bc85fc18da5a1aa34f9240ee\nSigned-off-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nSigned-off-by: Qian Yingjin <qian@ddn.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
